story.title: Dating App Mishap - Episode 4
story.storyDescription: When Lucy accidentally sends a racy photo of herself to her BFF, she wonders: Is HE the one for her?
story.creator: web-uploader

author.bio: Rebecca Brooks writes sexy contemporary romance with dirty-talking heroes, smart women, and happily ever afters. She lives in NYC and is always up for an adventure.

story.postPaywallNotification: Will Adam and Lucy choose friendship over romance?! Find out in DATING APP MISHAP.
